{"tid":1668453,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"3青年被11名黑衣人用木棍圍毆　清醒送院暫無人被捕","createTime":"2019-10-22T03:57:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T04:04:09.000Z","uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"57ef58e783713d0b74003687feb45f7f1b9ac972","tid":1668453,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T03:57:30.000Z","msg":"今日（22日）凌晨12時31分，3名青年在觀塘高超道38號對開，被11名黑衣人手及木棍襲擊，致姓郭的男子（15歲）頭及手部受傷；姓黃的男子（20歲）頭、腳及手受傷；姓黃（16歲）頭及手受傷。救護人員到場，3名傷者清醒送往聯合醫院治理。<br />\n<br />\n警方指，青年遇襲原因不明，經初步調查，案件列襲擊致造成實際身體傷害，交由觀塘警區刑事調查隊第6隊跟進，暫未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n警方又表示，施襲者為數11人，年約20至25歲，全為男性，案發時身穿黑衫黑褲。<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2479691/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2479691%2F&d=kAMrkm0lh8tAzahNx%2FKaSLZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=3935ed37\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2479691/</a>"},{"pid":"fd6de0990266f4410017211af18a6b0c5192a323","tid":1668453,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T04:02:18.000Z","msg":"插贓嫁禍之黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"647b3628a6b66e9a9e699b6b52a5c9639a48549a","tid":1668453,"uid":265168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T04:02:42.000Z","msg":"我屌。。。。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">想贏同我入嚟<br />\n想connect全世界同我入嚟<br />\n把握時機 食住個勢</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n[擴大戰線] [行動] 與其嘈加泰集會 不如唔搞呢個<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1668190\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1668190</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e896795ac03fbc78e56d9340f8c934275bae5561","tid":1668453,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T04:04:09.000Z","msg":"黑幫互鬥啫可能"}]}